            <li>Pairs beautifully with white, black, gray, and stained wood swings</li>
            <li>Excellent choice for pergola swings and covered patio swings</li>
          </ul>
          <h3>Chain Hanging Swing Ideas</h3>
          <ul class="bullet-list">
            <li>Creates a timeless traditional porch swing look</li>
